<item>
            <title>[LU-3106] create symlinks in procfs from ofd to osd</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3106</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;to preserve compatibility with pre-2.4 versions we should create few symlinks from /proc/fs/lustre/obdfilter/*/ to the corresponded OSD.&lt;br/&gt;
namely these are writethrough_cache_enable, readcache_max_filesize and read_cache_enable.&lt;br/&gt;
this way all the utilities (including 3rd party) keep working and the documentation is still valid.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
